repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The materials consist of formal portraits, group portraits, and reunion photographs of students and graduates of Yale College, Yale School of Law, Yale School of Divinity, Yale School of Medicine and the Sheffield Scientific School.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Class of 1909 freshman photograph gift of Nathan Marks, 2013. Accession 2017-A-059 gift of Anne Hall Connor, 2017. Accession 2018-A-047 gift of Carol Bertrand, 2017.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 10-A (YRG 10-A), Records of Yale College classes.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale Classes Photographs (RU 779). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The photographs are arranged in three series: I. Pictures of Yale Classes, 1806-1971. II. Oversize Pictures of Yale Classes, 1852-1970. III. Folio Pictures of Yale Classes, 1856-1960., and one addition.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of formal portraits, group portraits, and reunion photographs of students and graduates of Yale College, Yale School of Law, Yale School of Divinity, Yale School of Medicine, and the Sheffield Scientific School.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

separatedmaterial.p: Transfered to RU 684, Series 1, Box 14, Folder 536.
